# SafeStep public defaults — committed to the repo on purpose.
#
# These are the Supabase URL and ANON key. The anon key is *designed* to be
# public-facing — the actual access controls live in PostgreSQL Row-Level
# Security policies on the server. Treat this file like a config file, not
# a secret store.
#
# If you need to override locally (e.g. point at a different DB), create a
# .env.local — it overrides .env and is gitignored.

